      <title><![CDATA[Adolescent Sexual Experimentation Should Not Be a Crime [Commentary]]]></title>
      <link>https://cyh.rrchnm.org/items/show/45</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="element-set">
    <h2>Dublin Core</h2>
