      <title><![CDATA[The Trial of Stephen Arrowsmith (1678) [Trial Record]]]></title>
      <link>https://cyh.rrchnm.org/items/show/37</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="element-set">
    <h2>Dublin Core</h2>
